src:
Veja porque as vezes seu lanche chega misturado
01 Nov 2019, 19:23 by Joe



Temos que reconhecer que o talento desse cara pra dar grau com 3 xis salada na bagagem é de se admirar…
Se o lanche vier virado, pense que pelo menos valeu a pena.
Dica via Twitter @yoguinervoso e @indignada_sa.
text:
See why sometimes your snack arrives mixed
01 Nov 2019, 19:23 by Joe



We have to recognize that this guy's talent to grade 3 x salad in his luggage is a wonder…
If the snack comes over, think at least it was worth it.
Tip via Twitter @yoguinervoso and @indignada_sa.
